----------------------------------------------------S P A C E R   Q U E S T   G A M E   F O R M U L A E:----------------------------------------------------                      Condition of pods x number of pods Serviceable Pods  =  ----------------------------------                                      10-------------------------------------------------------------------------------Fuel and ETA-----------------       X = Drive type         |Y = Drive condition    |   ETA (Time) = (((21-X) + (10-Y)) x Z) + 10Z = Distance           |                       |   Fuel Required = ETA / 2                       |                       |   Fuel Cost  =  Fuel Required x 5-------------------------------------------------------------------------------         (value of cargo x distance PAY  =  (-------------------------  x  Serviceable Pods) + Fuel Cost + 1000         (           5-------------------------------------------------------------------------------B/F (Battle Factor) Determination---------------------------------components:     cabin (accomodations): ((cond +1) x str) / 10     life support system  : ((cond +1) x str) / 10     navigation system    : ((cond +1) x str) / 10      drive system         : ((cond +1) x str) / 10     robotic system       : ((cond +1) x str) / 10     hull                 : ((cond +1) x str) / 10                            ----------------------completed trips over 49 divided by 50number of battles won--------------------------------------------------Sum of all of the above then divided by 5 = B/F-------------------------------------------------------------------------------(updated 11/12/90)